===Noun===
{{en-noun|head=[[deoxyribonucleic]] [[acid]]|-}} (''abbreviation'' '''[[DNA]]''')

# {{label|en|genetics|biochemistry}} A [[nucleic acid]] found in all living things (and some non-living, see [[virus]]); consists of a [[polymer]] formed from [[nucleotide]]s which are [[shaped]] into a [[double]] [[helix]]; it is [[associated]] with the [[transmission]] of [[genetic]] [[information]].

